# Work Pulse Context

Copy this file to `context.md` in the same directory and fill in your real values.
`context.md` is gitignored and never checked in.

## GitHub
- Username: your-github-username
- Work org: your-company-org  (e.g. acme-corp)
- OSS / work-adjacent orgs: org-one, org-two

## Jira
- Site: yourcompany.atlassian.net
- Projects: PROJECT1, PROJECT2

## Paths
- Repos root: ~/path/to/repos  (all local git repos live under here)
- Obsidian daily notes: ~/path/to/vault/Periodic/Daily

## Slack
- Your user ID: UXXXXXXXXXX  (find in your Slack profile → "Member ID")
- Team channels: #eng-team-yourteam, #xfn-team-yourteam, #another-channel

## Confluence
- Team page: https://yourcompany.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SPACE/pages/PAGEID/Team+Name
- Sprint board: https://yourcompany.atlassian.net/jira/software/c/projects/ENG/boards/NNN
- Roadmap: https://yourcompany.atlassian.net/jira/polaris/projects/RM/ideas/view/NNNNNNN

## Team
- Manager: Your Manager (EM)
- PM: Your PM
- T2 Stakeholders: PM Two, PM Three
- Teammates: Teammate One, Teammate Two, Teammate Three, Teammate Four
